<h1>Assessment</h1>

<div>
<strong>Course Title:</strong> <%= @assessment.course.title %><br />
<strong>How did using collection materials complement your teaching goals?</strong> <%= @assessment.using_materials %><br />
<br />
<strong>In what ways was Houghton Library involved in your class? </strong>
<ul>
	<% @assessment.involvement.split(',').each do |i| %>
      <li><%= i %></li>
 	<% end %>
</ul>

<strong>Please evaluate how well the following met your teaching needs:</strong><br />
<strong>Reference staff expertise:</strong> <%= @assessment.staff_experience %><br />
<strong>Reference staff availability:</strong> <%= @assessment.staff_availability %><br />
<strong>Instructional space:</strong> <%= @assessment.space %><br />
<strong>Online request system for course:</strong> <%= @assessment.request_course %><br />
<strong>Online request system for materials:</strong> <%= @assessment.request_materials %><br />
<strong>Library catalogs (Hollis, OASIS, etc.):</strong> <%= @assessment.catalogs %><br />
<strong>Digital collections:</strong> <%= @assessment.digital_collections %><br />
<br />
<strong>Do you plan to involve Houghton Library in your teaching again?</strong> <%= @assessment.involve_again %><br />
<strong>If no, please tell us why not:</strong> <%= @assessment.not_involve_again %><br />
<strong>What could Houghton Library do to make your teaching with special collections better in the future?</strong> <%= @assessment.better_future %><br />

</div>
